label: codeSystemName
comment: The name of the code system corresponding to this observation.

label: codeSystemID
comment: An identifier for this Code System, which assigns specific, unique codes to the items listed in it. Use of Code Systems accepted globally or nationally, enable identifying the item (like soil, crop, pest, pesticide, fertilizer, geographical unit, PIN/ZIP Code, commodity, market, bank, language, HSN) across the entire ecosystem.

label: mediaURL
comment: Link(s) to any image(s) or media of the entity or incident corresponding to this observation

label: codeSystemStatus
comment: The operational status of the code system corresponding to this observation. For eg., draft, active, retired, experimental, unknown

label: versionInfo
comment: Information about the version of the entity corresponding to this observation

label: publisherInfo
comment: Details of the person/ organization which has published the code system corresponding to this observation.

label: isCaseSensitive
comment: Represents whether the codes in the code system or value set are case sensitive or not. True - if case sensitive, False - if not.

label: purposeDescription
comment: Descibes the purpose of the entity or service corresponding this observation.

label: copyrights
comment: Copyrights are legal protections that grant creators exclusive rights to control the use and distribution of their original work.

label: totalCount
comment: Total number of items in the entity corresponding to this observation.
